Package: typetomusic
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pyqt5
Recommends: python3-pynput, python3-evdev, python3-fluidsynth, fluidsynth, fluid-soundfont-gm | timgm6mb-soundfont, pipewire-audio | pulseaudio
Installed-Size: 248
Maintainer: TypeToMusic Contributors <typetomusic@example.com>
Description: Turn your keyboard into a musical instrument
 TypeToMusic captures every keystroke system-wide and plays a MIDI note
 in real time using FluidSynth. Supports multiple musical scales,
 GM instruments, and dynamic velocity from typing speed.
 .
 Features: global key capture, low-latency MIDI playback, scale selection,
 instrument selection, and an animated waveform visualiser.
